headline: Tuttle Capital Management Launches the Tuttle Capital Meme Stock Income Blast ETF (MEMY)
summary: Greenwich, Connecticut--(Newsfile Corp. - January 20, 2026) - Tuttle Capital Management, a leading provider of thematic and alternatives ETFs, today announced the launch of the Tuttle Capital Meme Stock Income Blast ETF (CBOE: MEMY), now trading on the CBOE.MEMY is an actively managed exchange-traded fund that seeks to provide current income and exposure to the equity performance of "Meme Stocks"-companies that gain significant popularity among retail investors through social media...
